  "gitCommitMessage": "feat: 10 features — goals, dashboard, water, history, charts, repeat, streak, AI edit, barcode, pricing\n\n1. Onboarding TDEE: body data flows through onboardingStore → TDEE calculated → saved to nutrition_profiles\n2. Dashboard: CalorieRing on diary tab, neutral gray (#94A3B8) when over goal — no guilt-tripping\n3. Water reminders: expo-notifications push every 2h with quiet hours (22-08), toggle in Settings\n4. History: existing diary with DateNavigator + [date].tsx already functional\n5. Charts: goal dashed line on WeeklyBarChart, neutral color for over-goal bars\n6. Quick repeat: \"Repeat yesterday's meal\" suggestion in empty MealSection slots\n7. Streak: toggle in Settings (OFF by default), conditionally shown on Stats tab\n8. AI correction: inline editing of ingredients (name, grams with auto-recalc), delete/add items, isEdited flag\n9. Barcode scanner: expo-camera barcode → Open Food Facts API → portion selector → save. MMKV cache. FREE for all users\n10. Pricing transparency: already implemented — prices on welcome screen, Free vs Pro comparison\n\nAlso includes: PostHog analytics + Sentry error tracking (GDPR-compliant, init after consent only)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
